00:19:06,170 --> 00:19:06,710
General.

288
00:19:06,710 --> 00:19:09,330
At a time like this,
focus on the greater good.

289
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:11,240
Pass my order.

290
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:14,420
Sharpen the sword

291
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:16,670
and fight with me.

292
00:19:16,670 --> 00:19:17,370
Aye!

293
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:50,260
Yuwen Yue, after the fight yesterday,

294
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:51,850
I understand something.

295
00:20:52,370 --> 00:20:53,880
When I first came here,

296
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,130
I thought

297
00:20:55,130 --> 00:20:56,240
I was exiled by Father.

298
00:20:57,060 --> 00:20:58,780
Now, I’ve realized

299
00:21:00,540 --> 00:21:02,410
I do not live for him.

300
00:21:02,670 --> 00:21:04,250
What is the point of hanging on

301
00:21:04,250 --> 00:21:06,120
to the vanity and scams.

302
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:08,320
This is the world

303
00:21:08,320 --> 00:21:10,010
that needs me.

304
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:12,200
I no longer fight just for my father

305
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:13,650
and the state,

306
00:21:13,850 --> 00:21:15,100
but for those civilians

307
00:21:15,100 --> 00:21:16,940
struggling at the border.

308
00:21:17,460 --> 00:21:20,230
People have to see the war
to understand that

309
00:21:20,550 --> 00:21:21,950
life is the most precious thing

310
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,660
in this world.

311
00:21:24,420 --> 00:21:26,800
Therefore, Yuwen Yue,

312
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:27,750
thank you.

313
00:21:31,470 --> 00:21:32,740
I should thank you.

314
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:35,520
What for?

315
00:21:36,100 --> 00:21:37,290
After this war,

316
00:21:38,780 --> 00:21:39,720
I find that

317
00:21:40,500 --> 00:21:42,130
I am not a straggler anymore.

318
00:21:43,780 --> 00:21:45,230
I will obey your order

319
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:46,590
and help you train the troops.

320
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:49,540
What is the point of training them?

321
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:51,530
No one wins

322
00:21:52,770 --> 00:21:54,780
in the war.

323
00:21:55,260 --> 00:21:57,520
There will be causalities on both sides.

324
00:21:57,910 --> 00:22:00,560
Death befalls all men alike.

325
00:22:03,930 --> 00:22:04,870
Yuwen Yue.

326
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:07,630
As the heir to the Eye of Intel,

327
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:09,360
you have great responsibilities.

328
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:12,750
This is not your battlefield.

329
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:15,040
A good spy

330
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:16,870
is equal to an army.

331
00:22:18,770 --> 00:22:20,700
Now, spies of Liang are everywhere.

332
00:22:21,130 --> 00:22:22,770
They even get documents

333
00:22:22,770 --> 00:22:24,160
issued by the court

334
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:26,490
sooner than I do.

335
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,820
And they’re behind

336
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:31,830
our recent failures.

337
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:37,610
Yuwen Yue, I understand that

338
00:22:37,720 --> 00:22:39,480
you went through a lot

339
00:22:39,950 --> 00:22:41,460
earlier in Chang’an.

340
00:22:42,220 --> 00:22:43,450
But don’t forget

341
00:22:43,450 --> 00:22:44,400
we’re men.

342
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:46,260
We have

343
00:22:46,260 --> 00:22:46,910
our own duties.

344
00:22:51,180 --> 00:22:52,770
Stop running away from them.

345
00:22:53,420 --> 00:22:54,680
You should go back.

346
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,290
Come out.

347
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:23,360
So annoying!

348
00:23:23,750 --> 00:23:25,230
Every time I want to play

349
00:23:25,230 --> 00:23:26,400
hide-and-seek with you,

350
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:28,470
you see right through it.

351
00:23:28,750 --> 00:23:29,840
Boring.

352
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:32,490
Princess.

353
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:35,850
What did you say?

354
00:23:36,470 --> 00:23:37,610
What did you call me?

355
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:39,660
Chun.

356
00:23:42,140 --> 00:23:43,250
Answer my question.

357
00:23:43,390 --> 00:23:44,640
Why didn’t you attend

358
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:45,680
my birthday ceremony?

359
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:47,460
I sent you an invitation.

360
00:23:48,190 --> 00:23:49,220
Forgive me, Princess.

361
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:51,700
What are you saying? What princess?

362
00:23:51,700 --> 00:23:52,600
Who is Princess?

363
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:53,750
Where is Princess?

364
00:23:55,210 --> 00:23:57,910
Chun, I was held up by an emergency.

365
00:23:57,910 --> 00:23:59,500
What emergency could it be?

366
00:24:03,190 --> 00:24:04,080
I knew it!

367
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:05,960
You were avoiding

368
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:06,970
Wei Shuyou and the others.

369
00:24:07,510 --> 00:24:09,100
He just finished his confinement.

370
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:10,650
I didn’t know

371
00:24:10,650 --> 00:24:12,190
he’d come.

372
00:24:16,050 --> 00:24:17,820
Yan Xun,

373
00:24:18,010 --> 00:24:20,850
don’t be mad at me.

374
00:24:22,630 --> 00:24:24,780
I wouldn’t dare.

375
00:24:24,780 --> 00:24:26,750
Why are you always calling me Princess?

376
00:24:28,740 --> 00:24:29,860
Yan Xun.

377
00:24:30,170 --> 00:24:31,130
Are we still friends

378
00:24:31,130 --> 00:24:32,140
or not?

379
00:24:32,140 --> 00:24:33,700
Don’t treat me as a stranger.

380
00:24:36,620 --> 00:24:38,500
Today is my birthday

381
00:24:38,690 --> 00:24:40,180
and you didn’t come to see me.

382
00:24:40,180 --> 00:24:42,200
I had to come here instead.

383
00:24:44,510 --> 00:24:46,850
I am a noble princess of Wei.

384
00:24:46,850 --> 00:24:48,220
During the ceremony,

385
00:24:48,220 --> 00:24:50,260
those noblemen present

386
00:24:50,670 --> 00:24:53,460
liked me so much.

387
00:24:54,080 --> 00:24:55,690
But Yan Xun,

388
00:24:55,910 --> 00:24:57,020
why couldn’t you like me

389
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:58,590
even for a moment?

390
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:01,760
Our identities are different.

391
00:25:01,980 --> 00:25:04,000
I hate this difference.

392
00:25:04,850 --> 00:25:06,170
Couldn’t we get along

393
00:25:06,170 --> 00:25:07,470
like what we did in our childhood?

394
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:11,040
Do you remember when I was nine,

395
00:25:11,040 --> 00:25:12,480
we snuck out of the Palace?

396
00:25:13,260 --> 00:25:14,910
Then we hung out on the streets,

397
00:25:14,910 --> 00:25:16,400
eating snacks

398
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:18,010
and having so much fun.

399
00:25:18,010 --> 00:25:19,740
We even got into a fight.

400
00:25:24,150 --> 00:25:25,410
But now...

401
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:28,040
You are reluctant to

402
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:29,870
call my name.

403
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,590
I was young and naive at that time.

404
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:37,330
Forgive me, Princess.

405
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:39,300
Yan Xun,

406
00:25:39,300 --> 00:25:40,310
if you go on talking to me like this,

407
00:25:40,310 --> 00:25:41,520
I will be mad.

408
00:25:41,670 --> 00:25:42,930
I will stop talking to you.

409
00:25:43,090 --> 00:25:43,870
I shall leave.

410
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:46,370
Please wait, Princess.

411
00:25:47,070 --> 00:25:47,750
Ajing.

412
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:01,330
This is my gift for your birthday.

413
00:26:01,610 --> 00:26:02,520
It’s just a little something.

414
00:26:02,520 --> 00:26:03,920
I hope you can take it.

415
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:12,430
You prepared a gift for me?

416
00:26:29,870 --> 00:26:31,710
It’s Huanhuan’s tail.

417
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:37,630
I heard that

418
00:26:37,790 --> 00:26:39,090
Huanhuan bit your fingers

419
00:26:39,090 --> 00:26:39,850
the other day.

420
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:41,320
Noble Concubine killed it

421
00:26:41,320 --> 00:26:42,100
and threw it out.

422
00:26:43,380 --> 00:26:44,590
You cried for a long time.

423
00:26:45,390 --> 00:26:46,430
So I had my men

424
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:47,890
find the rabbit

425
00:26:48,050 --> 00:26:49,620
and cut off its tail

426
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:50,600
as a memorial.

427
00:26:50,980 --> 00:26:52,180
I’d appreciate it

428
00:26:53,100 --> 00:26:54,600
if you could accept it.

429
00:27:00,140 --> 00:27:01,240
Usually,

430
00:27:01,870 --> 00:27:03,580
others give me pearls and gold.

431
00:27:03,580 --> 00:27:04,860
It’s nothing new.

432
00:27:05,910 --> 00:27:06,980
With this tail,

433
00:27:07,120 --> 00:27:08,560
I’ll feel as if

434
00:27:08,560 --> 00:27:09,210
Huanhuan didn’t leave

435
00:27:09,210 --> 00:27:10,650
and would always be with me.

436
00:27:12,730 --> 00:27:13,940
Yan Xun,

437
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:14,750
this is the best gift

438
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:15,960
that I’ve ever had.

439
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:16,910
Thank you.

440
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:20,060
I’ll leave then.

441
00:27:20,510 --> 00:27:21,810
See you later.

442
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:33,280
Ajing.

443
00:27:36,430 --> 00:27:37,510
Burn this.

444
00:27:38,190 --> 00:27:39,670
Aye, Your Excellency.

445
00:28:03,770 --> 00:28:04,850
What are you drawing?

446
00:28:06,080 --> 00:28:07,500
It’s a secret.

447
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:15,410
Eat some when you have time.

448
00:28:33,770 --> 00:28:34,600
Your Excellency.

449
00:28:34,790 --> 00:28:36,360
Message from Mr. Wu says

450
00:28:36,360 --> 00:28:38,070
he has been recruiting in Yanbei.

451
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:39,210
And he’ll help you return to the north

452
00:28:39,210 --> 00:28:40,590
in Chang’an.

453
00:28:45,120 --> 00:28:46,070
Your Excellency,

454
00:28:46,690 --> 00:28:48,430
I know that you

455
00:28:48,430 --> 00:28:49,600
tell everything to Miss Chu.

456
00:28:50,180 --> 00:28:53,240
However, this is too important.

457
00:28:53,930 --> 00:28:55,210
Please...

458
00:28:59,380 --> 00:29:00,310
Achu?

459
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:03,200
Our secret is safe with her.

460
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:18,180
What is it

461
00:29:18,180 --> 00:29:20,000
that’s hidden in your bag?

462
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:21,350
Can’t you tell me now?

463
00:29:29,770 --> 00:29:30,610
Isn’t it...

464
00:29:30,900 --> 00:29:32,630
The legendary Triple Crossbow?

465
00:29:34,090 --> 00:29:35,620
I saw it in the Yuwen’s Mansion.

466
00:29:36,380 --> 00:29:37,630
And I made some adjustments to it

467
00:29:37,630 --> 00:29:38,120
according to the layout

468
00:29:38,120 --> 00:29:39,620
of the Oriole Courtyard.

469
00:30:19,170 --> 00:30:20,070
Careful!

470
00:30:26,860 --> 00:30:27,870
Don’t mess with me.

471
00:30:27,870 --> 00:30:29,090
Go to sleep.

472
00:30:47,120 --> 00:30:48,450
I’ve been grounded for two years.

473
00:30:48,450 --> 00:30:49,740
It’s killing me.

474
00:30:50,030 --> 00:30:51,620
This is so much fun!

475
00:30:51,860 --> 00:30:53,390
Thanks to Yan Xun,

476
00:30:53,590 --> 00:30:55,540
your place has become a prison.

477
00:31:13,780 --> 00:31:17,550
I must revenge!

478
00:31:19,150 --> 00:31:21,140
Three years will soon expire.

479
00:31:21,810 --> 00:31:23,890
Take action now, or it’ll be too late.

480
00:31:24,930 --> 00:31:27,820
If, by any chance,
His Majesty releases Yan Xun,

481
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,580
that’ll be bad news.

482
00:31:31,580 --> 00:31:34,220
Whether His Majesty releases him or not,

483
00:31:34,220 --> 00:31:37,000
he must die.

484
00:31:39,990 --> 00:31:44,430
A long delay means trouble.
The sooner the better.

485
00:31:48,580 --> 00:31:51,900
= Weipin Pavilion =

