00:31:51,900 --> 00:31:53,210
Ms. Wei,

487
00:31:53,610 --> 00:31:55,360
I’ve long heard about your reputation.

488
00:31:55,990 --> 00:31:56,950
In order to

489
00:31:56,950 --> 00:31:58,560
find this kind of dress,

490
00:31:58,560 --> 00:31:59,920
I’ve been to almost every store

491
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,500
in the city.

492
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:02,630
People say

493
00:32:02,630 --> 00:32:04,580
only your store sells it.

494
00:32:04,790 --> 00:32:06,400
It’s true.

495
00:32:06,930 --> 00:32:08,430
Your reputation is well-deserved.

496
00:32:08,430 --> 00:32:10,010
Where do you purchase this kind of dress?

497
00:32:11,250 --> 00:32:12,610
From the south.

498
00:32:12,610 --> 00:32:13,380
We have

499
00:32:13,380 --> 00:32:14,620
everything here,

500
00:32:14,620 --> 00:32:16,510
and it is of the best quality.

501
00:32:16,510 --> 00:32:17,360
Also, we have special offers

502
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:18,610
from nine to eleven.

503
00:32:18,610 --> 00:32:19,780
You’ll enjoy

504
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:20,820
a 90 percent discount

505
00:32:20,820 --> 00:32:21,630
on this outfit.

506
00:32:21,630 --> 00:32:23,090
And we can deliver it to your place.

507
00:32:23,090 --> 00:32:23,960
There will be new arrivals from the south

508
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:26,050
in a few days.

509
00:32:26,050 --> 00:32:28,470
They can only be found here.

510
00:32:28,470 --> 00:32:29,950
It’s truly good.

511
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:30,920
However,

512
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,280
the weather is bad today.

513
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:34,460
You’d better close down earlier,

514
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:35,650
so as not to let the rain

515
00:32:35,650 --> 00:32:37,020
ruin these

516
00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:37,970
exquisite goods.

517
00:32:38,290 --> 00:32:39,720
I’ll take these.

518
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:42,600
Please send them to this address.

519
00:32:42,600 --> 00:32:43,700
Rest assured.

520
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:45,060
They will arrive tomorrow morning.

521
00:32:45,060 --> 00:32:46,880
Take care.

522
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:47,550
Sure.

523
00:33:01,370 --> 00:33:02,920
Your Excellency. Achu.

524
00:33:03,380 --> 00:33:04,730
Wei Shuyou is out.

525
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:06,900
The first thing

526
00:33:07,150 --> 00:33:08,700
that idiot did

527
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,240
was to cause us trouble.

528
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:12,590
We have to

529
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:13,990
get rid of him later.

530
00:33:15,220 --> 00:33:16,430
Why later?

531
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,720
This time is the time.

532
00:33:18,940 --> 00:33:22,220
= Oriole Courtyard =

533
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:11,080
How many people on earth are here?

534
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:12,910
We got the wrong information.
What should we do?

535
00:35:12,910 --> 00:35:13,620
Let’s get out of here.

536
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:38,060
= Pine Hall =

537
00:36:00,160 --> 00:36:01,470
Finally, it’s all gone.

538
00:36:02,040 --> 00:36:04,190
Worrying over the thief is worse
than theft.

539
00:36:06,180 --> 00:36:06,950
Your Excellency,

540
00:36:07,260 --> 00:36:08,740
the next three months

541
00:36:08,950 --> 00:36:09,710
will be tough.

542
00:36:19,270 --> 00:36:20,530
Those noble families are not going to

543
00:36:20,530 --> 00:36:21,780
give up easily.

544
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:24,690
Enemies are lurking in the dark.

545
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:26,770
We can’t sit and do nothing.

546
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:29,420
Do we have any ways to counterattack?

547
00:36:29,420 --> 00:36:30,760
So we have to deal with

548
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:32,660
Yuwen, Wei and Zhao,

549
00:36:32,930 --> 00:36:34,210
the three noble families at the same time.

550
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:38,090
The Imperial Mausoleum
of the late emperor.

551
00:36:40,020 --> 00:36:41,700
We can start from the mausoleum

552
00:36:41,830 --> 00:36:43,400
to play them off against each other.

553
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:44,440
Kill three birds with one stone.

554
00:36:45,440 --> 00:36:46,380
But those three

555
00:36:46,380 --> 00:36:47,680
have no overlaps in business.

556
00:36:47,810 --> 00:36:49,060
Where should we start?

557
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:52,110
Who built the Mausoleum,

558
00:36:52,110 --> 00:36:53,510
and who provided the building materials,

559
00:36:53,510 --> 00:36:55,420
and now, who are watching over it?

560
00:36:55,420 --> 00:36:57,230
Yuwen Huai is the guard.

561
00:36:57,430 --> 00:36:59,130
The Zhao family built it

562
00:36:59,130 --> 00:37:00,290
with materials

563
00:37:00,290 --> 00:37:01,120
from the Wei family.

564
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,570
If someone broke into the Mausoleum,

565
00:37:02,570 --> 00:37:04,270
none of them can get away from it.

566
00:37:05,230 --> 00:37:06,160
That’s true.

567
00:37:06,860 --> 00:37:09,030
Their power has been expanding,

568
00:37:09,300 --> 00:37:11,140
posing a threat to imperial power.

569
00:37:11,430 --> 00:37:13,150
Emperor has been eager to

570
00:37:13,150 --> 00:37:14,240
find fault with them.

571
00:37:14,450 --> 00:37:15,390
What we need to do is

572
00:37:15,390 --> 00:37:17,090
to advance the dog-eat-dog fight.

573
00:37:17,850 --> 00:37:18,910
Problem is

574
00:37:19,670 --> 00:37:21,250
Yuwen Huai is at the Mausoleum.

575
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:22,470
Achu,

576
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:24,430
we should be more careful

577
00:37:24,430 --> 00:37:25,420
and wait for the right time.

578
00:37:27,930 --> 00:37:29,260
That may come

